        'You are the Head of Regulatory Affairs at Perdana Commerce Bank Berhad. Using this Teams meeting recap together with BNK_03_Credit_Risk_Policy.docx and the Covenant Monitor tab in BNK_01_Group_Loan_Portfolio.xlsx, assess whether the meeting reflects policy-consistent decision making on waivers, restructures, and watchlist escalation. Highlight where management debate suggests control uncertainty or inconsistency between business and risk teams. Flag control concerns requiring immediate escalation as Red, issues needing documented follow-up as Amber, and policy-consistent discussion points as Green. Present as a RAG table.',
