        'You are the Group Chief of Staff at Perdana Commerce Bank Berhad. Research the latest BNM and regional supervisory commentary relevant to the issues visible in the Loan Book Summary and Covenant Monitor tabs of BNK_01_Group_Loan_Portfolio.xlsx, draft a 2-page OneDrive brief titled "BNM Bilateral Readiness - Commercial Banking", email it to the CEO, CFO, CRO, and Head of Regulatory Affairs, and schedule a 30-minute prep meeting for tomorrow morning. Ask Cowork to place a one-page summary at the front of the brief that flags immediate review items as Red, this-week follow-ups as Amber, and stable areas as Green. Present as a RAG table.',
